{"_response_info":{"status":"ok"},"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/soil-protection-review.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/soil-protection-review","title":"Soil Protection Review","format":"transaction","updated_at":"2013-01-09T13:05:32+00:00","details":{"need_id":"B951","business_proposition":true,"description":"Online tool for completing your annual farm soil management and protection review if you claim Single Payment Scheme payments","language":"en","alternative_title":"SPR assesment","more_information":"<p>This tool uses <a href=\"/government-gateway\" title=\"Government Gateway\">Government Gateway</a>. </p>\n\n<h2>Getting help</h2>\n<p>Contact the Farming Advice Service if you have any queries about the <abbr title=\"Soil Protection Review\">SPR</abbr>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Farming Advice Service</strong><br />\n0845 345 1302 <br />\nMonday to Friday, 9am to 5pm</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Keeping a copy on your farm</h2>\n<p>You don&rsquo;t have to complete the review online. Instead, you can keep a copy on your farm. Either:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>use a <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://rpa.defra.gov.uk/rpa/index.nsf/contentdocs/08B7386AAEECC830E8025768E0058A46E\" title=\"Soil Protection Review - spreadsheet template\">spreadsheet</a></li>\n  <li>Download, print out and complete the latest version (<abbr title=\"Soil Protection Review\">SPR</abbr> 2010)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://rpa.defra.gov.uk/rpa/index.nsf/0/c39ae2bb7b8ab8158025768e005e57cd/$FILE/Soil%20Protection%20Review%202010.pdf\" title=\"Download 'Soil Protection Review 2010: guidance and forms' (PDF, 766KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘Soil Protection Review 2010: guidance and forms’ (PDF, 766KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Agents</h2>\n<p>Sign up as an <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://secure.services.defra.gov.uk/wps/portal/wfa/!ut/p/c5/04_SB8K8xLLM9MSSzPy8xBz9CP0os3gzdx8LQyd_A0t3X3dHA08fM1fvAEdXY3cTI6B8JE55A3dDSnQbmBHQHQ5yLX7b8cmDzAfJG-AAjgb6fh75uan6BbmhEQaZAekAekimGQ!!/dl3/d3/L2dBISEvZ0FBIS9nQSEh/\" title=\"Sign up as an agent for Defra farm surveys and assessments\">agent</a> if you want to use the Soil Protection Review for more than one farmer.</p>\n\n<h2>Cross compliance</h2>\n<p>These standards are part of <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://rpa.defra.gov.uk/rpa/index.nsf/UIMenu/814240C66F10CAC8802570C7004248D4?Opendocument\" title=\"Cross compliance (Rural Payments Agency)\">cross compliance.</a> You must meet them to get your farming subsidy under the <a href=\"/single-payment-scheme-online\" title=\"Manage your Single Payment Scheme online\">Single Payment Scheme</a>. </p>\n\n","introduction":"<p>The Soil Protection Review (SPR) is part of <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://rpa.defra.gov.uk/rpa/index.nsf/UIMenu/814240C66F10CAC8802570C7004248D4?Opendocument\" title=\"Cross compliance (Rural Payments Agency)\">cross compliance.</a> Completing the SPR online is quicker, easier and reduces your chances of an inspection.</p>\n","will_continue_on":"Defra farm surveys and assessments","link":"https://secure.services.defra.gov.uk/wps/portal/wfa/!ut/p/c5/04_SB8K8xLLM9MSSzPy8xBz9CP0os3gzdx8LQyd_A0t3X3dHA08fM1fvAEdXYwNTI6B8JG55AzMCusNB9uFW4W6OXx5kPkjeAAdwNND388jPTdUvyI0wyAxIVwQAzhGtrA!!/dl3/d3/L2dBISEvZ0FBIS9nQSEh/","alternate_methods":"\n","minutes_to_complete":"","expectations":["Available in England only"]},"tags":[{"title":"Farming","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/business%2Ffarming.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Health and safety, registering and licensing animals, compliance tools","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=business%2Ffarming","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/business/farming"},"parent":{"title":"Businesses and self-employed","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/business.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Information about starting up and running a business in the UK, including help if you're self 